d around without getting spanked severely by other roaming bandits.<br>
<br>
i had some questions and would much appreciate the feedback of some knowledgable and gracious person.  i realize there are a lot, but perhaps responses to a few of them could get me heading in the right direction.<br>
<br>
- does hide work after your attacked by someone in PvP on Rallos?<br>
<br>
- when you get to level 10 does the attitude of most players change re random and sporadic PKs ?  ie.  do you get ganked less often ?<br>
<br>
- what are the chances that a assassin camper would let me loot the DE mask on Rallos (man! i really need the MR! roots and rooting pets suck!). and are there any other dirt cheap or free MR equipment to be had.<br>
<br>
what are some good piercing/slashing/1HB weaps a rogue of levels 1 to 10 can cull without tons of cash (less than 17 plat)?<br>
<br>
is the grouping situation above level 10 similar to that on blue servers ?  or are most people too afraid to group because of the moments of weakness (low health) it presents to other potentially unscrupulous individuals ?<br>
<br>
at the risk of being flamed, if anyone would like to trade me resources on Rallos for resources on Veeshan, give me a tell.  a small leg up wouldn't be terribly bad right now as i don't know a single person on Rallos.<br>
<br>
thanks in advance..<br>
<br>
pestylenz<br>
42 rogue of Veeshan<br>
5 rogue of Rallos<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elegance>Elegance</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/8/01 11:01:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rallos </span><hr size=1> the pking (ganking) doesnt slow down til 20th or so. the mask can be a royal pain on rallos, I tried 3 different times to go get mine and it was uncamped for 30 or so hours (combined attempts) but once there was somone in there I had no troubles getting one.<br>
<br>
go to velius and sneak around the uthork camps you can get a free walrus tooth easy. if you take yer 17 plat you should be able to get a bs fang also.<br>
<br>
want some cash? hmmmm youll have to dig up my post on faction, then go to high pass and sell notes  14 for 50 pp is a good price, just make sure to bring a 4th lvl chanter or somone who can inivs others. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://members.theglobe.com/kambic/box.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/8/01 11:43:38 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rallos </span><hr size=1> Coming from a 40 rogue on RZ, I'd suggest you delete the character and play on Sullon instead, it's much better.<br>
