 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukinthaf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kinthaf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/14/01 12:03:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rallos </span><hr size=1> I really don't see how you can make those comments Aerimus.<br>
<br>
1. How do you not have control on Rallos?  More so than most servers you can determine your fate.  True there is more risk, but isn't that why you play pvp?<br>
<br>
2. What do you do on any other server when you get trained?  petition? (haha).  On Rallos...keel them.  [Yes trainning is the most unbalencing pvp aspect, but I don't see how it would be any different on another pvp server]<br>
<br>
3. Sure there are some high level grieffers, and some guilds/players that don't exactly play fair, but for the most part by 50+ you should really be in a guild you can trust, or at least have good friends to back you up.   And whats the difference between a bully and a pvp'er?  The two are not mutally exclusive...<br>
<br>
Rallos has its share of problems, and I'm not sure if I would start a new char on it over SZ, but its really not that bad.  I am acually having more alot more fun these days than pre50 pvpwise. <p>Kinthaf, RZ
